{"tid":618613,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"成日講人工智能AI，你地工作上用緊黎做咩？","createTime":"2018-04-06T03:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T14:54:15.000Z","uid":52090,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"15ad5df1b38ce0ae1cba75db423df9569cbeb5aa","tid":618613,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係個 IT狗，<br />\n<br />\n呢兩年做唔少 人工智能 AI Solutions<br />\n<br />\n係香港，你地工作上多數係咩地方運用 AI？<br />\n<br />\n（AI = Deep Learning / Reinforcement Learning）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拋磗引玉：<br />\n<br />\n1. 智慧都市，睇人睇車，睇有冇意外，幫助City Planning同埋緊急服務<br />\n<br />\n2. 商場博物管人流管理，方便佢地Plan舖／展品，加租，同管理保安<br />\n<br />\n3. 大學，做智慧校園，管飯堂，做分流<br />\n<br />\n4. 幫工廠做ＱＣ，睇下出貨有冇問題；仲有睇機器做Alert<br />\n<br />\n5. 幫個倉做Inventory，唔洗再用手入<br />\n<br />\n（終於有香港份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n6. 幫Trading公司搵相似嘅貨，攞去Sell客<br />\n<br />\n7. 做Operations Planning，每日點安排，D Staff會做Ｄ咩"},{"pid":"1f619d3b2c0afde868f15d7e3f1f130d530f1d18","tid":618613,"uid":38253,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"多數上連登覆下post待機等吩咐咁啦"},{"pid":"a07a90846c6b7dc83d4898c0333cca27d7cc1ee8","tid":618613,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"覆樓主"},{"pid":"c0a6cb48fd8bc8533763358617ce505972b678bf","tid":618613,"uid":179239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得 AI 唔只 Deep Learning / Reinforcement Learning. 哩啲都只係Data Science 既層面。<br />\n不過照哩個Trend 行，有Data在手就係皇者。"},{"pid":"7cdc6ede5526abb5ff61c7aa28ccc6cc34baabd5","tid":618613,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"工作上無用但想用"},{"pid":"d2ea331596251b696b82e6d013fa518f34c3f492","tid":618613,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0a6cb48fd8bc8533763358617ce505972b678bf","tid":618613,"uid":179239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score